              ***** RSTR     ARR             ARR    WB WEB    Strauss K                20   13    0
                 A 330 : P - MUS-A 100 with a grade of C or better
                 Hybrid course designed to give practical hands-on experience
                 recording, mixing, and mastering music. Oriented towards
                 students studying music or media who need to be proficient in
                 audio production. Coursework includes online reading, videos,
                 and guided production exercises, along with a weekly
                 instructor-led lab and student-produced final recording and
                 mixing project
                 This class requires a Recording Arts Fee. Current rates are
                 available at http://go.iu.edu/BLfees
                 Laboratory (LAB)
